          "body": "Filed from the pd-book-tools deep code/security review.\n\n    Report: `pd-book-tools/docs/research/2026-05-22-deep-code-security-review.md`\n    Finding: #11\n\n    ## Summary\n\n    LayoutRegion and PageLayout are documented public API and have to_dict/from_dict, but schema emission omits them.\n\n    ## Impact\n\n    Downstream codegen receives schemas for OCR/geometry but not the public layout JSON shape.\n\n    ## Evidence\n\n    - `docs/usage/public-api.md:52`\n- `docs/usage/public-api.md:57`\n- `pd_book_tools/schemas/emit.py:37`\n\n    ## Acceptance\n\n    - [ ] Add LayoutRegion and PageLayout to schema emission.\n- [ ] Add tests asserting enum values, fields, and round-trip shape.\n\n    ## Notes\n\n    This issue was filed from a read-only review. Confirm behavior with a focused failing test before implementation where practical.",
          "closed_at": "2026-05-22T16:04:00Z",
